{"tid":1745693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［檢討］黎明行動下民意有逆轉跡象，黎明不合昨運動要開始暫停！！","createTime":"2019-11-22T10:48:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T00:21:23.000Z","uid":219007,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6d44c5e7ec448c13d46ddb3d9de541d5a245f2bb","tid":1745693,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:48:36.000Z","msg":"多個民意調查顯示，在阻人返工行動後支持政府的民意有所微升，大家要警惕！！<br />\n<br />\n閒日由其朝早不合昨運動事實令某些港人反感，呢個係無得爭辯，要嬴就要好討好呢班中間派，若果再沉迷黎明行動呢埸革命隨時完結！！<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，所有朝早不合昨運動需立即叫停，重回文宣工作先，再檢討黎明行既可行性先好再推行！！！<br />\n<br />\n蕭生今次批中！<br />\n<br />\n個人卑微的請求停火14日 希望各界回應及討論〈蕭若元：蕭氏新聞台〉<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/whnEAMwOVhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwhnEAMwOVhk&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRyloRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=c3daa122\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/whnEAMwOVhk</a>"},{"pid":"b43f82e0da7e3db03d8b77624f21919793f4ee9a","tid":1745693,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:11:01.000Z","msg":"戰役過後，痛定思痛，認清現實，重新出發(抗爭五部曲-前言)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742018\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742018</a>"},{"pid":"8abdcfc810e20e97f9c90fd95c5fcb87578db7d0","tid":1745693,"uid":78184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T16:45:17.000Z","msg":"推，民意轉向開始"},{"pid":"d1bf3a8bd404e2996198e3e1a2f832b7ee9919f8","tid":1745693,"uid":37528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T16:55:38.000Z","msg":"要諗下辦法點轉型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a69c9b94701b3f62e0234e74e993544b74e9b8","tid":1745693,"uid":74182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T16:57:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"12b2943a59b6e65d665f81641d68e3865895695f","tid":1745693,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T16:59:06.000Z","msg":"好彩嘅係就黎區選<br />\n見大家似乎都係回緊氣等投票 絕對正常<br />\n亦可以襯呢個